'''Nabil Emad Aly Elmahdy''' ({{langx|ar|نبيل عماد علي المهدي}}; born 6 April 1996) also known as '''Donga''' ({{langx|ar|دونجا}}), is an Egyptian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]] for [[Saudi Pro League]] club [[Al-Najma SC (Saudi Arabia)|Al-Najma]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].<ref name="Soccerway"/>

==Club career==
Emad started his career at [[Baladiyat El Mahalla SC|Baladiyat El Mahalla]], then played for [[Grand Hotel FC|Grand Hotel]], [[El Gouna FC|El Gouna]], MS Aga and [[Beni Ebeid SC|Beni Ebeid]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2020/7/1/رحلة-نبيل-دونجا-من-بلدية-المحلة-إلى-ميت-عقبة-إنفوجراف/4855438 |title=رحلة نبيل دونجا من بلدية المحلة إلى ميت عقبة.. إنفوجراف |publisher=youm7.com |language=ar |date=1 July 2020 }}</ref> In 2016, Emad was transferred from Beni Ebeid, a team in the [[Egyptian Third Division]], to [[Pyramids FC]] (then known as Al-Assiouty Sport) for 40,000 Egyptian pounds. He signed a 5-year contract.<ref>{{cite web|title=بالصور.. الأسيوطى يضم دونجا "بنى عبيد" مقابل 40 ألف جنيه|url=http://www.youm7.com/story/2016/5/14/%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%88%D8%B7%D9%89-%D9%8A%D8%B6%D9%85-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%86%D8%AC%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D9%86%D9%89-%D8%B9%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%AF-%D9%85%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%84-40-%D8%A3%D9%84%D9%81-%D8%AC%D9%86%D9%8A%D9%87/2717661|website=اليوم السابع|accessdate=26 September 2017|language=ar-AR}}</ref> On 3 February 2026, Nabil Emad joined [[Saudi Pro League]] club [[Al-Najma SC (Saudi Arabia)|Al-Najma]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://x.com/alnajmahfc/status/2018472496593535008|title=نبيل عماد دونجا نجماوي💚⭐️}}</ref>

==International career==
He made his debut for the [[Egypt national football team]] on 23 March 2019 in an [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations qualification Group J|Africa Cup qualifier]] against Niger, as a starter.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Confederation of African Football]]|url=http://www.cafonline.com/en-us/competitions/32ndeditionoftotalafricacupofnations/MatchDetails?MatchId=yhPLwkqNSe4OmjvXeZ8cF%2bOvbNd2WsyxXJkyaFdphGJAFgwmNeI25zyoMHpDrT0%2b|title=Niger v Egypt game report|date=23 March 2019}}</ref>

== Personal life ==
On 29 May 2026, just hours before Egypt's head coach [[Hossam Hassan]] announced the [[2026 FIFA World Cup squads#Egypt|final World Cup roster]] featuring Nabil Emad 'Donga', an Italian woman stated via Instagram that she was taking legal action against the player for an alleged physical assault. The incident in question reportedly occurred in July 2025.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.alarabiya.net/arab-and-world/egypt/2026/05/30/%D8%A7%D9%8A%D8%B7%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%AA%D8%AA%D9%87%D9%85-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B5%D8%B1%D9%8A-%D9%86%D8%A8%D9%8A%D9%84-%D8%B9%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AF-%D8%AF%D9%88%D9%86%D8%AC%D8%A7-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%87%D8%A7|title=إيطالية تتهم لاعب الكرة المصري نبيل عماد "دونجا" بالتعدي عليها|date=29 May 2026|website=العربية}}</ref>

